Dear U2.COM member,

Feb 7th, 2001: Registered members of U2.COM have an opportunity to
participate in a pre-sale of tickets for the BUFFALO, NEW YORK date of U2?s
upcoming Elevation 2001 Tour in North America.

This show, which takes place on May 31st, goes on public sale from Saturday
February 10th.

As a registered member of U2.COM, in this e-mail you will find a USER NAME
and a PASSWORD. From 10am local North American time on Wednesday February
7th, a limited number of tickets will be on sale to U2.COM members who
provide these details to tickets.com

This offer is for two tickets to one show.

We can't promise to satisfy everyone but this gives you an improved
opportunity to get the first tickets on sale. (As previously mentioned,
please keep your password confidential - and please, if you are
unsuccesful, do not risk your cash with scalpers.)


********* User Name: tickets
                 Password: newyork01 ************


The direct link for ticket sales is http://www.tickets.com/u2.html

(this will be live on Wednesday 7th)

1. U2.com members can contact TICKETS.COM online from Wednesday FEBRUARY
7TH at 10am (your local North American timezone) for the opportunity to
purchase a maximum of 2 tickets.

2. You will need to provide THE USERNAME and the secure password provided
to you by U2.COM in this email.

3. Only tickets for the U2 show dates in BUFFALO, NEW YORK as listed above
will be available for this offer.

4. We have a limited number of tickets in the different ticket
prices available. They are available on a first come first served basis.
We apologise in advance if you are unsuccessful in obtaining a ticket for
the show you require. Please note you will have the opportunity to buy at
the public on sale on SATURDAY Feb 10TH.

5. TICKETS.COM's convenience and handling charges apply to all orders.

6. If you have not previously registered for YOUR Account on TICKETS.COM,
you can pre-register all of your billing information with TICKETS.COM
before the on sale by clicking on the link below.

